@startuml Sequence_Interface

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Theme Manager" as Theme
participant "Component Library" as Components

== Page Load ==
User -> Client: Access application
Client -> Client: Load Tailwind CSS
Client -> Components: Load UI components
Components --> Client: Components ready
Client -> Theme: Check theme preference
Theme --> Client: Theme mode
Client -> Client: Apply theme styles
Client -> Client: Load icons (Lucide)
Client -> Client: Initialize animations
Client --> User: Render UI

== Theme Toggle ==
User -> Client: Toggle dark mode
Client -> Theme: Update theme preference
Theme -> Theme: Save preference
Theme -> Client: Apply new theme
Client -> Client: Update CSS variables
Client --> User: Display new theme

== Component Interaction ==
User -> Client: Interact with component
Client -> Components: Handle interaction
Components -> Components: Update state
Components -> Components: Apply animations
Components --> Client: Updated component
Client --> User: Show feedback

== Responsive Update ==
Client -> Client: Detect screen resize
Client -> Client: Update breakpoint
Client -> Client: Adjust layout
Client --> User: Responsive layout

@enduml

